lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F173858_2818501c61bc922f9be37435b69535fb.jpg&h=f49b7a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/173909_8107692fa21b565f5b25ff37a7f83929.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F173909_8107692fa21b565f5b25ff37a7f83929.gif&h=b13890cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7327687e4a75dd3a75e6c0fcb297bb4ed7e5c4ea","tid":748421,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"點解中國咁鍾意用數字嚟命名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好俗氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080186f06d2538554bf1ced39c5e990cf3013136","tid":748421,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英國著名歷史<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>學家李約瑟的《中國科學技術史》<br />\n<br />\n2018好危險, 你返去歷史啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>問題係，李約瑟既理論響歷史學界已經冇人理<br />\n根本就算響古代，中國既科技發展比起希臘羅馬阿拉伯果邊都冇優勢可言<br />\n到左近代同現代，中國更加落後西方一大截<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nobel_laureates_per_capita\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNobel_laureates_per_capita&d=MPR8sQOOPtB75xu9CZ45TcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a7222d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nobel_laureates_per_capita</a><br />\n中國人均諾貝爾獎科學類獎項只有每1000萬人0.035個獎<br />\n係所有國家包尾，仲低過印度</blockquote>支那人有個自我安慰既講法<br />\n話係因為支那既科研遲起步<br />\n<br />\n而外國大學咁多科研成果係因為多支那留學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有幾多個中國留學生移民外國之後拎到Nobel Prize？十隻手指數唔數得曬？</blockquote><br />\n科研喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2018年仲用緊古代四大發明打飛機"},{"pid":"6428791151864a6bb562ea643356fbfe9e227386","tid":748421,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二，「中國拒絕公平貿易」說法，亦是有「錯！」。華春瑩指，中方一直主張公平貿易，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現正</span></span>推進新一輪對外開放，將繼續努力營造開放、透明、公平及可預期的商業環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝晒喎，入左世貿幾多年？</blockquote><br />\n透明喎公平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}